'''Sébastien Kamba''' (wavutse ku ya 25 Ukuboza 1941), niUmukinnyi wa firime [[Kongo|muri  Kongo]] .  Umwe mu bakora amafilime yambere mu nganda za firime zo muri [[congo]], yayoboye filime ngufi ku bufatanye n’abakora amafilime y’Abafaransa. 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 25 Ukuboza 1941 i Brazzaville, muri [[Kongo|Repubulika ya Kongo]] .

== Umwuga ==
Yimukiye mu [[Bufaransa]], yiga mu biro bishinzwe ubufatanye bwa Radiofonique . Nyuma yaje kwimenyereza umwuga kuri tereviziyo i Paris ndetse anaba umwarimu.  Mu 1964, Kamba yakoze filime yambere yimpimbano ya [[Congo Brazzaville|congo]], film ngufi ya politiki ''Le Peuple du Congo-Léo vaincra'' . Yakozwe ku bufatanye n’itangazamakuru rya tereviziyo.

Mu 1966, yakoze ''Kaka yo nayo ngufi'' hanyuma ''Mwana keba''  muri 1970.  Mu 1973, Kamba yayoboye filime ya mbere yagaragaye muri Repubulika ya [[Kongo]]: ''Al Rançon d'une alliance'', yakuwe mu gitabo cyitwa 'La légende de Mfoumou Ma Mazono' cyanditswe na Jean Malonga.  Mu 1992, yasohoye igitabo ''Cinématographique et Parti Unique'' (Cinematographic Production and Unique Party. Urugero rwa Kongo). 

Ku ya 1 Gashyantare 2019, i Brazzaville habereye igikombe cya mbere cy’ibikombe bya sinema muri [[Congo]] cyiswe "Les Kamba's Awards" mu rwego rwo guha icyubahiro Kamba. 

